Building mobile app


cordova platform add android
cordova plugin add phonegap-plugin-push --variable SENDER_ID="SENDERID"
cordova build (buils apk)
cordova run android (installs on device through usb)


Installing development environment on Fedora 24

NODE + CORDOVA

# dnf install nodejs
# dnf install npm
# npm install -g cordova


ANDROID SDK

Download sdk from [1] and uncompress to /opt.
Configure path
Install java-devel





[1] https://developer.android.com/studio/index.html
